        {
            "title": "天文台｜今日有幾陣驟雨 早上沿岸有霧 日間最高氣溫約28度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/31aeaa940155af7192c8a3afe7a2afd6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041807353415566.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股較為潮濕的偏南氣流正影響廣東沿岸。本港今早沿岸有霧，橫瀾島的能見度曾下降至1000米以下。此外，一道雲帶覆蓋華南沿岸。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上沿岸有霧。日間短暫時間有陽光及炎熱，最高氣溫約28度。吹輕微至和緩偏南風。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201835/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上沿岸有霧。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ede455a1ce836f6f3a8f6e12a8112fd4/2025-04/22_4.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上沿岸有霧。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201836/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/328462df94db06f2d45b82bcea278312/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-18_at_12_30_50_AM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201837/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28fd258c02c5418151642b3591f31e06/2025-04/Screenshot_2025-04-18_at_12_31_02_AM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201838/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上沿岸有霧。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08e557176f47296a5f2b3f0ce546695b/2025-04/23_4.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上沿岸有霧。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201839/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上沿岸有霧。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7304e0729395f94a209db7cb163ca820/2025-04/24_2.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上沿岸有霧。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>展望未來一兩日部分時間有陽光，有一兩陣驟雨。下週初大致天晴，日間炎熱。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
